description:
I just hanged a new shower curtain but my "detailed" 6yr-old noticed something else.
Funny in my eyes it was just flower print and pollen of flowers but in this little guy's eyes they resemble CORONAVIRUS!! :) 

"Tantanan nyo nga kami coronavirus...Pati sa shower curtain present at sikat kayo?! Hehe..."

LIKE. SHARE. SUBSCRIBE.
- Thanks,  JN Tube -
